<div id="about-container" class="container policy">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col col-12">
      <header>
        <h1><%= title "About" %></h1>
      </header>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col col-12 col-sm-4">
      <div class="headshot-container">
        <%= image_tag 'about-julian.png',
          alt: 'Portrait of Julian',
          class: 'headshot' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col col-12 col-sm-8">
      <p>Julian Tigler is from Charlotte, NC, and currently lives in Seattle, WA. He's developed software for tech giants, startups, nonprofits, and solar companies.</p>
      <p>Julian is inspired by the brave people who brought us the two-day weekend, the 8-hour work day, overtime pay, and an end to child labor. He hopes to make them proud by helping employees everywhere majorly improve their work lives.</p>
      <p>Feel free to <%= mail_to @email, 'send him a message' %> at any time!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
